/a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionstart_event\"><code>transitionstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcechanged_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcechanged</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcedown_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcedown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforceup_event\"><code>webkitmouseforceup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcewillbegin_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcewillbegin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/wheel_event\"><code>wheel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p><b>localName</b> zwraca lokalną część uściślonej nazwy węzła.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><i>nazwa</i> = element.localName\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>nazwa</code> to ciąg z lokalną nazwą węzła (zobacz <a href=\"#uwagi\">Uwagi</a> poniżej, aby dowiedzieć się więcej)</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<p>(Musi obsługiwać treść XML typu, jak &lt;tt&gt;text/xml&lt;/tt&gt; lub &lt;tt&gt;application/xhtml+xml&lt;/tt&gt;.)</p>\n<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">&lt;html xmlns=\"<span class=\"nowiki\">http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml</span>\"\n      xmlns:svg=\"<span class=\"nowiki\">http://www.w3.org/2000/svg</span>\"&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n  &lt;script&gt;&lt;![CDATA[\n  function test() {\n    var text = document.getElementById('text');\n    var circle = document.getElementById('circle');\n\n    text.value = \"&lt;svg:circle&gt; has:\\n\" +\n                 \"localName = '\" + circle.localName + \"'\\n\" +\n                 \"namespaceURI = '\" + circle.namespaceURI + \"'\";\n  }\n  ]]&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n&lt;body onload=\"test()\"&gt;\n  &lt;textarea id=\"text\" rows=\"4\" cols=\"55\"/&gt;\n  &lt;svg:svg version=\"1.1\"\n    style=\"width:100%; height:100%; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; z-index:0;\"\n    viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\"&gt;\n    &lt;svg:circle cx=\"50\" cy=\"50\" r=\"30\" style=\"fill:#aaa\" id=\"circle\"/&gt;\n  &lt;/svg:svg&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Dla węzłów typu innego niż <code>ELEMENT_NODE</code> i <code>ATTRIBUTE_NODE</code> oraz dla węzłów utworzonych za pomocą metod DOM Level 1, jak na przykład <code><a href=\"pl/DOM/document.createElement\">document.createElement</a></code>, własność ta ma zawsze wartość <code>NULL</code>.</p>\n<p><b>localname</b> węzła to ta część uściślonej nazwy węzła, która znajduje się po dwukropku. Uściślone nazwy są zwykle używane w XML jako część przestrzeni nazw w poszczególnych dokumentach XML. Na przykład w uściślonej nazwie \"ecomm:partners\" nazwa lokalna to \"partners\", a \"ecomm\" to prefiks.</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;ecomm:business id=\"soda_shop\" type=\"brick_n_mortar\"&gt;\n  &lt;ecomm:partners&gt;\n    &lt;ecomm:partner id=\"1001\"&gt;Tony's Syrup Warehouse\n    &lt;/ecomm:partner&gt;\n  &lt;/ecomm:partner&gt;\n&lt;/ecomm:business&gt;\n</pre>\n<p>Prefiks - w tym wypadku \"ecomm\" - określa przestrzeń nazw, w której można użyć nazwy lokalnej.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"pl/DOM/element.namespaceURI\">element.namespaceURI</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Core-20001113/core.html#ID-NodeNSLocalN\" rel=\" noopener\">localName </a></p>\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"localName zwraca lokalną część uściślonej nazwy węzła.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element.localName","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element.localName","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Element.localName","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Element.localName","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.localName","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Element.localName","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/element/localname","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/element/localname/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element/localName","title":"element.localName"}],"pageTitle":"element.localName - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}